DTSTAMP:20260522T200000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20201002T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20201002T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:The Board held a closed session to conduct the Superintendent's Evaluation\, reviewing the performance of the district's chief administrator.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2020-10-02/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2020-10-02/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
