DTSTAMP:20260522T200000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20201007T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20201007T210000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Study Session)
DESCRIPTION:The Board held a Study Session on Distance Learning/In Person Learning to discuss instructional approaches and considerations for student learning during the pandemic.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2020-10-07/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2020-10-07/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
