DTSTAMP:20260522T200000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210127T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210127T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:The Board held closed sessions to discuss real property negotiations for 750 Bradford Street with the Sobrato Foundation\, as well as labor negotiations with CSEA and RCTA. The Board also approved multiple Measure T Bond Program projects including construction and modernization work at Orion Alternative School\, Clifford School\, Roy Cloud School\, Roosevelt School\, Adelante Selby School\, and Hoover School\, and took action on the Governing Board's Initial Proposal for 2021-22 negotiations with RCTA.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-01-27/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-01-27/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
END:VEVENT
