DTSTAMP:20260522T200000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210212T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210212T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Retreat (Offsite))
DESCRIPTION:The Board held a retreat focused on strategic planning\, including closed session discussions on budget negotiations and workforce housing\, followed by open discussions on equity work and a comprehensive review of the district's mission\, goals\, and beliefs.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-02-12/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-02-12/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
