DTSTAMP:20260522T200000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210224T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210224T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:The Board held closed sessions to discuss CSEA and RCTA negotiations\, approved multiple Measure T Bond Program projects including kindergarten bathroom remodels and asphalt replacement at Hoover Community School\, and discussed COVID-19 response and iReady Diagnostic Exam Results. The Board also conducted first readings of Board Policy 1340 - Access to District Records and Board Policy 3280 - Sale or Lease of Property.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-02-24/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-02-24/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
