DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20210324T210000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Study Session)
DESCRIPTION:The Board held a study session to receive an update on the Equity Consciousness Committee and discuss its ongoing work and initiatives.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-03-24/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2021-03-24/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
