SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board received the Special Education study report and implementation plan — a significant review of SPED services and recommendations. Approved Measure S bond program updates and Key Analytics financial tracking system for bond spending. Adopted Resolution 10 for TK teacher certification standards. Approved Measure U applications for McKinley\, Taft\, Clifford\, and KIPP.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-04-17/
