SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board approved Quattrocchi Kwok Architects for the Facilities Master Plan — the planning effort that would guide Measure S bond spending. Heard results of the Panorama school climate survey showing changes from fall to spring. Approved theatrical lighting for McKinley\, bond program consent items\, and outdoor education and summer program agreements.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-05-22/
