SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board recognized international staff and heard Connect Community Charter School's annual presentation. Adopted Resolution 11 for year-end budget transfers and approved the Prop 28 arts education expenditure plan. Ratified the RCTA teacher contract tentative agreement. Approved school plans for student achievement and Declaration of Need for substitute staffing.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-06-05/
