DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20240620T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Public hearings on the draft LCAP and proposed budget for 2024-25. Board adopted the meeting calendar\, approved Measure U disbursements\, and ratified agreements for mental health services (Effective School Solutions)\, after-school programs\, and community partnerships.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-06-20/
