SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Start-of-year meeting with a large consent calendar: 27 agreements for the new school year covering counseling\, tutoring\, after-school programs\, charter school facilities\, staffing agencies\, and food services. Approved the LCAP Federal Addendum\, CSEA tentative agreement\, food service bids\, and new personnel. Quarterly Williams Report confirmed compliance.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-08-07/
