DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20240828T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board discussed the Facilities Master Plan progress and the process for appointing an Area III trustee to fill a board vacancy. Public hearing confirmed sufficiency of instructional materials. Adopted resolutions for instructional material sufficiency and certificated tenure. First reading of the board vacancy bylaw. Notably\, Board received information that they had decided against placing a parcel tax on the November 2024 ballot.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-08-28/
