SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board discussed Measure S bond program priorities with a focus on HVAC replacements across the district. Heard an update on the Budget Renewal Initiative. Adopted Resolution 5 in favor of statewide Proposition 2 (school facilities bond). First reading of Board Bylaw 9223 on filling board vacancies. Reviewed charter school budgets.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-09-11/
