DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20241009T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board appointed a new Area III trustee from candidate presentations — filling the vacancy left by a departed board member. Approved consent items including a WestEd MOU and One Life Counseling amendment.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-10-09/
