DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20241023T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board heard the annual Health and Wellness report. Five policy first readings on absences\, parent notifications\, concepts/roles\, lactation accommodation\, and school websites. Reviewed unaudited actuals for all three charter schools and the HR department's hiring season preparations. Approved agreements with Redwood City Together and special education service providers.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-10-23/
