DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20241030T210000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Study Session)
DESCRIPTION:Study session focused on the Budget Renewal Initiative — the Board's strategy for addressing structural budget deficits through a combination of cuts and new revenue (eventually leading to the parcel tax effort).\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-10-30/
