DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20241120T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board held a public hearing on a design-build lighting retrofit project and approved Resolution 9 for an energy services agreement with Southland Industries. Heard an update on the workforce housing project at 750 Bradford St. North Star Academy presented. Eight policy first readings on school trips\, employee safety\, leaves\, modified duty\, and technology use. Adopted organizational meeting date and continued state preschool funding.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2024-11-20/
