SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Orion School presented. Board held a public hearing on the Connect Community Charter School renewal petition. Adopted Resolution 15 to apply for zero-emission school bus incentive (ZESBI) grants. Accepted CSEA union sunshine proposal and began classified employee negotiations for 2024-26. Received a recommendation for Imagine Learning math curriculum for grades 6-8.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2025-01-15/
