DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250226T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board received a Facilities Master Plan update and the annual LCAP update. Passed Resolutions 16-20 covering certificated administrator reassignment\, certificated and classified staff reductions\, TK teacher certification standards\, and teaching assignment options. Approved school safety plans and multiple Measure U addenda for Roy Cloud\, Orion\, and North Star.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2025-02-26/
