DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250312T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250312T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board discussed a citizens' initiative parcel tax alongside a potential district-sponsored measure. Approved HVAC equipment purchases from Daikin and Carrier for summer 2025 projects. Henry Ford School presented. Adopted the Imagine Learning Illustrative Mathematics curriculum for grades 6-8. Approved KIPP Measure U application and wireless access points through E-Rate.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2025-03-12/
