DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250326T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250326T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board renewed the Connect Community Charter School for another term after a public hearing. Approved the Second Interim Budget Report and the 2024 School Accountability Report Cards (SARCs). Second readings for sale of district property\, transportation\, and chronic absence/truancy policies. Approved new combi ovens for the school nutrition program. Clifford School presented.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2025-03-26/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2025-03-26/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
