DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250402T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250402T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Board Meeting)
DESCRIPTION:Board approved an agreement with TeamCivX and Godbe Research to study parcel tax feasibility — the first formal step toward what would become the 2026 Measure E campaign. McKinley School gave its annual presentation. Approved Phase 2 solar change orders with Holt Renewables and Chromebook purchases for incoming 6th graders.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2025-04-02/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2025-04-02/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
