DTSTAMP:20260522T200000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260513T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260513T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Regular)
DESCRIPTION:The Board was scheduled to consider multiple infrastructure and sustainability initiatives\, including approval of agreements for 8 EV chargers at Hoover Community School and Roy Cloud School through PowerFlex\, plus installation agreements with Atlas Pellizzari Electric ($70\,520) for chargers at Adelante Selby\, Clifford\, and Kennedy Schools. The agenda also proposed discussions of school plans for North Star School and Henry Ford School\, migration of district servers to Microsoft Azure Cloud Services via Looking Point\, and approval of numerous board policies related to student conduct\, health benefits\, and academic programs.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2026-05-13/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2026-05-13/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
END:VEVENT
