DTSTAMP:20260522T200000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260527T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260527T220000
SUMMARY:RCSD Board Meeting (Regular)
DESCRIPTION:The Board was scheduled to consider multiple facility improvement agreements for HVAC Upgrade projects Phase 2 at Clifford\, Orion\, and Kennedy Schools\, as well as an amendment to the geotechnical services agreement for the Solar Phase II Project. The agenda also proposed discussion of the district's Imagine Mathematics (IM) Three-Year Implementation and Sustainability Plan and approval of numerous curriculum and operational board policies.\n\nFull agenda and recordings: https://rcsd.info/meetings/2026-05-27/
URL:https://rcsd.info/meetings/2026-05-27/
LOCATION:District Office, 750 Bradford St, Redwood City, CA 94063
